response.overview: Enter heated combat in the aerial arena. Jets howl through the skies, engaging their enemies with every weapon and evasive maneuver at their disposal. Fly along with the top guns as they go head-to-head and wing-to-wing on the horizon. You'll feel as though you're strapped into the cockpit with these pilots. Feel the adrenaline pumping as the action heats up the heavens and the pulsing soundtrack sets the furious pace.
response.tagline: Suit up & strap in for high flying adventure!
response.title: Sky Wars
